gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Pelicans 110, Thunder 106
gameRecap.excerpt: The Pelicans defeated the Thunder, 110-106. CJ McCollum recorded 29 points, 11 rebounds, and five assists for the Pelicans, with Zion Williamson adding 20 points, nine rebounds, and eight assists in the victory. Chet Holmgren tallied 19 points, 11 rebounds, and three assists for the Thunder in the losing effort. The Pelicans improve to 3-1 on the season, while the Thunder fall to 3-2.
